<details class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-200 border border-base-300 mb-3">
  <summary class="collapse-title font-semibold text-secondary text-sm">Receiving a dividend</summary>
  <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-base-content/80 space-y-2">
    <p>Members will be notified via email when a new dividend has been issued.</p>
    <p>Once issued, members can choose to have their dividend paid out or can recontribute their dividend towards the next week's pool.</p>
    <p>In order to request a pay out, a <%= link_to 'PayPal.Me', 'https://www.paypal.com/au/digital-wallet/send-receive-money/paypal-me', target: '_blank', class: 'link link-primary' %> handle needs to be entered in the <%= link_to 'Membership', membership_path, class: 'link link-secondary' %> section.</p>
    <p>All dividends will be automatically recontributed back into the pool if not claimed by the <%= ConsolidationDate::DAY_OF_THE_WEEK %> following a distribution.</p>
  </div>
</details>
